# Platform

## Description
A brief description of your project.

## Requirements

To run this project, you need to install the following SDL2 libraries:

- SDL2
- SDL2_image
- SDL2_mixer
- SDL2_ttf

## Installation Instructions

### In Linux environment

You can install the necessary libraries using the following command:

```bash
sudo apt-get install libsdl2-2.0-0 libsdl2-dev libsdl2-image-dev libsdl2-mixer-dev libsdl2-ttf-dev